Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.99,0:02:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to write manga \Non my own from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.86,0:02:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.48,0:02:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,W—Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.04,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it should be pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You fail if you can't make your deadlines, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll take it back, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you hanging \Nout there with Miyoshi, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got that part wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I couldn't finish the name \Nisn't because I was with Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's just the opposite.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.15,0:03:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten pretty serious about her.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to write \Nsomething that'll be successful.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.96,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's kind of like you and Azuki \Nwaiting until your dreams come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Love takes many different forms.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't start out doing this for a girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.91,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I think I'm just like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I did have the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.14,0:03:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.06,0:03:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's true, then you really \Ncan't miss your deadlines.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a manga writer no matter what.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I have to team up with somebody else.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But your names—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They look like crap, so let me \Nknow when you finish one.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll clean it up for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.66,0:03:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody else will understand what you wrote.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.02,0:03:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, it'll cost you 100 yen each.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.54,0:04:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Also,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.13,0:04:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm working on my own,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.46,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to change Ashirogi Muto to Ashiro Muto.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.77,0:04:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you just use your real name?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.27,0:04:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.98,0:04:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.89,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The opening ceremony is gonna start soon!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.49,0:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was nervous about the new term, so I overslept.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's lame.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's both do our best.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.76,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—Yeah—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Mashiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.39,0:04:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault for not keeping my promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No it's not!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.62,0:05:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.99,0:05:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you spent the entire break with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent time together,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was writing scenarios \Nthe whole time, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.79,0:05:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need to do is to tell Mashiro \Nand I'm sure he'll understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.53,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, it'll just \Nsound like I'm making excuses.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't tell Azuki, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So please don't say \Nanything unnecessary, alright?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.88,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He already knows it wasn't your fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like everything is over!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still going to be a manga writer!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And Saiko will keep going, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.73,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep working \Nhard because I like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I {\i1}can{\i0} work hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Saiko too, and he understands.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you like me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.01,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say anything to \Neither of them, I'll hate you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,B—But—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to do it alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you guys fight or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not that immature.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.68,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a name yet, but I \Ncame up with an idea for a story.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.69,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
