Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.48,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A con artist detective who sets up traps \Nfor criminals to discover the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do the story right,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it could definitely be interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.94,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,But to pull this off,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.99,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,won't he need Takagi's help?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've given up on mainstream battle manga?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also pretty mainstream, so—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.62,0:06:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is much more suited \Nto Ashirogi Muto's style, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the coffee's getting to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.19,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you guys decide to split up?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.15,0:07:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him I'd have a name ready by the end of \Nsummer break, but I couldn't finish it in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro sure is strict.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's just really serious about what he's doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.16,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I also started thinking I wasn't very \Nsuited to writing a battle manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.41,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro seemed really set on doing one, so \NI guess we just weren't on the same page.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.63,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm writing a mystery.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A mystery?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible to have \Nyou take a look at my name?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.51,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mashiro doesn't know that \Nyou're writing a mystery right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.87,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell him I decided \Nto write something different.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.85,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I had planned on telling him \Nafter I finished it this summer,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't get it done in time,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.19,0:07:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll try and become a manga writer on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.27,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What's with these two?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.70,0:07:58.28,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,If I tell Takagi what Mashiro \Nis working on right now—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.04,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, a mystery is good.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It suits you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and bring it in.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you tell me to hurry,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any ideas for the main character.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.69,0:08:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make the main \Ncharacter a normal detective.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is the \Ntricks and how they play out.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.71,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talented.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.73,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always telling you that the whole \Nediting department thinks so too, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be confident in yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,O—Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yujiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Crow's on the cover of volume 49.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing, Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're at Niizuma's place, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give him the phone for a second?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, that was a bit rude of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I just get you to fax your name in?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.66,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to meet in person?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda, you're always like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, I guess that's what I like about you—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is great.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.75,0:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Write me a name.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your biggest strength is your drawings,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so make sure you focus on \Nfinding a style that fits the story.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.23,0:09:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You alone today?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, could it be—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That you guys split up?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.37,0:09:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who does the drawings, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.95,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for somebody to do the drawings \Nfor the runner-up in the latest "Story King."
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.92,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're interested—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't have him!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.07,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll get back to work.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The runner-up for the latest "Story King."
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.23,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to do the art and get it serialized, it would most likely be popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If something is good, of course it'll be serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.86,0:09:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you say you want to,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go apologize right now and ask him for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.23,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,If something is good, it'll be serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.15,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And if I get serialized—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,if you do that,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to team up with Takagi anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still want want to do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Team up with me and write manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to draw the pictures
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's going to write the stories.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.21,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fu—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,sion!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.22,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-stop to the finish line!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not sure
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.99,0:10:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what I should do yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.83,0:10:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you aren't sure, then I don't think it's a good \Nidea to team up with somebody else just yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Takagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of sudden, but can you come in tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.32,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I actually asked you here \Nto talk about Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to answer honestly.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you completely against \Nteaming up with him again?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who asked him \Nto team up in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.87,0:11:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I want to work together.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.49,0:11:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it's my fault things ended up this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.95,0:11:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to write something that will \Nmake him want to work with me again.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he manages to get serialized on his own.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.79,0:11:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do what I say,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.29,0:11:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you two back together
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.16,0:11:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll make a hit manga for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.43,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that you and Mashiro \Nare both on the exact same page.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say that you couldn't write \Ndifferent manga even if you wanted to.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure what you—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.53,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Mashiro is trying to come \Nup with a detective story of his own.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.40,0:12:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.12,0:12:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you tell Mashiro what I'm working on right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.58,0:12:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised that two \Npeople who decided to split up
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,both decided to write the same kind \Nof story without telling each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.00,0:12:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,could you keep this a secret until you're \Nabout to graduate and write a mystery—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.37,0:12:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a name for whatever \NMashiro is trying to come up with?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.68,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it a secret?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.68,0:12:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro is always trying to \Nrush into getting serialized, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.81,0:12:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But a detective story should \Nhave a little more time put into it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.69,0:12:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for the next two years, \Nlet's work on a name together.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.62,0:12:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But, wouldn't that be like lying to Mashiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how it works at Jack right now:
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.03,0:12:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make a one-shot that's popular \Nenough, they let you serialize it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.95,0:12:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you submit just three interesting chapters for \Na serialization meeting, they let you serialize it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.87,0:12:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that this leads \Nto many new series ending early.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's especially hard on new artists.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.54,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But for a while now, I've been wanting to put \Nsome extra time into a series to make it great.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.76,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But the only ones who can do \Nthat right now are you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you a deadline of six months \Nto come up with a battle manga,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you're going to go \Nwith this, that doesn't apply.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Spend as much time as you can \Non this for the next two years
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.39,0:13:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and then get Mashiro to draw it for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can make something amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in getting serialized \Nwhile you're still in high school
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,if it just ends up getting cancelled anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.74,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So while you still can, spend time \Non making something perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.70,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure that Mashiro doesn't team up \Nwith anybody else or get serialized by himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mashiro manages to get serialized on his own,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then shouldn't you let him do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked to Mashiro yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it looked like part of \Nhim still wants to work with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.93,0:13:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he turned down doing the drawings for the\N runner-up name in the latest "Story King" contest.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.94,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's so, is there any \Nreason to not tell Mashiro—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.44,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, Mashiro will \Npush to get serialized right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For his sake—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, for both of your sakes,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.23,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you should make a name that you've \Nhad a lot of time to think about.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.21,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the character that Mashiro \Nhas been thinking about is—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.04,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say any more, I'll just end up trying to \Nwrite a name that matches Mashiro's character.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try and win something \Nlike "Story King" on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.30,0:14:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if Mashiro says he's okay \Nwith getting back together, we will.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said makes a lot of sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.90,0:14:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I think too much like an adult.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to come \Nup with something interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.82,0:14:52.94,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.74,0:14:58.16,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Even if Mashiro tells Takagi that he's \Ntrying to come up with a detective story,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.82,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Takagi won't say anything \Nabout what he's writing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.13,0:15:04.29,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Even if it takes all he's got, he'll \Ndefinitely bring in an interesting mystery.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too weird to see you guys not working together.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.41,0:15:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever it takes to help you guys make up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we're fighting or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me what I can do to help!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, it's alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.33,0:15:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, names really are difficult.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin sure is amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How's he always do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I make names?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.55,0:15:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First, he thinks up everything in his head,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.96,0:15:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then writes the dialogue out on the computer,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.84,0:16:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and then turns that into the pages and panels?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.04,0:16:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched him do it all summer long on my computer,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.64,0:16:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's how I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If even Shuujin wasn't able to do that much,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.78,0:16:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,then I wonder if I'll be able to.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't think you can, just get back toge—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.32,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still going to try.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I have to do it alone, \NI've decided to do it for Azuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it no matter what!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm saying—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you'd figured something out,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.25,0:16:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but I haven't heard anything \Nabout you for two months.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually writing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.11,0:16:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going slowly, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.31,0:16:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a one-shot in the next issue.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I submitted it for serialization.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.47,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't exactly get rejected, but they \Nmade me try it out as a one-shot first.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, the editing department just \Ndoesn't have an eye for greatness.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.52,0:16:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's still good news, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not great at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.16,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't do well, there \Ngoes my shot at a series.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.50,0:17:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, and ever since last time, \NNakai has really gotten serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.46,0:17:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure what it's about, but the \Nart definitely isn't name level.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a painting or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.42,0:17:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have only been for a bit, \Nbut you worked with us too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're also part of Team Niizuma—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Team Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'd better try harder \Nso we can all change Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Fukuda?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.88,0:17:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.63,0:17:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No slacking off.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.50,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Fukuda and Nakai are both doing names.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.36,0:17:37.23,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And it's a late night show again,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.95,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,but Azuki got another regular role.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.16,0:17:44.50,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Can I really become a mangaka?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? They split up?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.92,0:17:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.35,0:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi told me not to make you worry, but I—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.98,0:18:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was 100 yen each, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you clean these up for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote a name?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only five, but yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You finished five?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.66,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Wow, I haven't even finished one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:24.75,Book,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H888D90&\frz18.6\an7\fs30.083\blur1.003\move(133.333,244.009,148,283.452)}"Transparent Detective Skeleton"\N(Tentative Title)
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.37,0:18:23.64,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,A detective?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.64,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a name.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.91,0:18:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's it a detective story?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.19,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Hattori tell you I was trying \Nto come up with a detective story?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.20,0:18:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't find out until about a \Nmonth after I'd started writing my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.13,0:18:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the idea when I saw a cellphone novel \Nwebsite that was looking for mystery stories.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, it was the day you called \Nme when I was at Miyoshi's place.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.89,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same day I quit as Eiji's assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also the same day I came up with \Nthe idea to write a detective story.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.91,0:18:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.11,0:18:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that you and Mashiro \Nare both on the exact same page.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Great minds think alike, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.37,0:19:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So we both came up with the \Nsame thing on the same day?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're such idiots!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I could almost cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori sure is sly.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.51,0:19:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no way I could keep \Nyou in the dark for two years.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to hide it from Azuki and Miyoshi as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.78,0:19:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we say to him?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be honest and go back to \Nthe way we've been doing it—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's just the easy way out.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.28,0:19:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We ended up like this because I couldn't \Nfinish the name and you got mad at me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.40,0:19:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm not really that mad.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.08,0:19:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the reason you didn't finish the name \Nwas because you were just hanging out with Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I know I was wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was just jealous of her.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.26,0:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I also realized one more thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.65,0:20:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we fool Hattori?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Us, fool him?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.42,0:20:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We let him think that we're still working separately
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.81,0:20:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and just keep telling him that we can't come \Nup with anything for about six months.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.28,0:20:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we use that time to come up with not \Nthree, but ten names ready for serialization.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.09,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori said to think about it for two years,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.95,0:20:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can't wait that long.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.37,0:20:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's definitely a better idea to spend \Nmore time thinking if it's a detective story,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but two years is just too long.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My condition is six months.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.46,0:20:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We take our time and work on a name together.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.13,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's good. I like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fool Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just like the detective \NI've been thinking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,R—Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's decided, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly what Hattori had in mind, was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.78,0:21:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Hattori said it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.19,0:21:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A mangaka must be able to surpass his editor.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he did.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We were only split up for a month, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems a bit short, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no reason to split up in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've figured that out, \Nlet's head over to the studio.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.92,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see your character design.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.04,0:21:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.75,0:21:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.09,0:21:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you guys try talking again?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.89,0:21:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi Muto is supposed to be the \Ndreams of two becoming one, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already talked about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.10,0:21:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting back together.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we made you worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.68,0:21:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so worried that I cried!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading to the studio \Nnow, so I'll make it up to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.15,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna come?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.91,0:21:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh—oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.12,0:21:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.37,0:21:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda told Miho that the two of you split up.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.53,0:21:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to say anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.07,0:21:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho was really worried this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.64,0:22:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But she told me not to interfere with anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.88,0:22:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.63,0:22:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sending her a message apologizing for \Nmaking her worry and to say we're back together.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Send.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.32,0:22:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, that was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:34.04,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6D6D96&\fs60.167\blur1.003\move(813.333,73.537,813.333,-46.796)\frz-19\fax-0.1}Azuki Miho
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:34.04,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\c&H706E8E&\fs36.769\blur1.003\move(893.333,185.18,893.333,64.846)\frz-19.5\fax-0.08}Back\NTogether
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:34.04,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\c&H877B89&\fs36.1\blur1.003\move(180,474.648,180,354.315)\frz-20.5\fax-0.06}I'm so relieved. Good luck! I'm a little jealous that\Nyou and Takagi are more in sync than we are, though.\N*lol*
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.66,0:22:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what'd she say?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.37,0:22:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you can read it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.96,0:22:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.85,0:22:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She says you are on the same wavelength?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.99,0:22:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.16,0:22:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always wondered "Why am I the only one having a hard time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,doushite boku dake ga kon'nani tsurai no ka to itsumo omotteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The people around me all seemed so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mawari no hito bakari shiawase sou ni mieta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But when I talked to you, I felt just a little bit better
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,dakedo kimi to hanashitara sukoshi dakedakedo ki ga raku ni natta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because we were open with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,nita youna koto uchiakete kuretakara kana
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the reality you can't see with your eyes is like a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kao no mienai genjitsu ga toki ni kaibutsu no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our ambitions are crushed, but we move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,bokura no kokorozashi wo tsubusou to oshiyosete kurukeredo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can say from the bottom of my heart that I'm glad I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,deaete yokatta to kokoro kara ieru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,People are multiplying little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hito ga sukoshi zutsu fuete ku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,While clenching their warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sono nukumori wo kamishimenagara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could support each other or face the boring things head on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sasae attari hikutsu wo butsuke attari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll finally arrive at that place alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hitori ja tadori tsukenai basho ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:57.33,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}We're now proceeding en route
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:57.33,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}bokura wa ima kitto omomuite iru tochuu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:06.42,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}en route
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:06.42,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}tochuu
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.97,0:24:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is a detective story.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:18.97,Next Ep,,0,0,0,,{\pos(80,80.222)\blur0.334\clip(63,78,1163,234)}Next\NEpisode
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.35,0:24:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How was my "Skeleton: The Transparent Detective?"
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.13,0:24:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective stories make great mainstream manga!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.87,0:24:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about my "Skeleton?"
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.51,0:24:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.35,0:24:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: Cooperation and Conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:29.99,Next Ep,,0,0,0,,{\pos(113.333,46.796)\blur0.334\clip(49,47,643,198)}Cooperation and \NConditions
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.27,0:24:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams come in many forms.
